The paper discusses low rank tensor completion for visual data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The methods discussed in the paper involve optimization models and algorithms, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also includes numerical experiments, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT).
